Date of Birth: August 2, 1897<br/>
Birthplace: Preston, Idaho, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: October 11,1945<br/>
Death: December 13, 1953<br/>
<br/>
Born Aug. 2, 1897, at Preston, Franklin Co., Idaho, to Matthias Foss Cowley and Abbie Hyde.
Ordained apostle Oct. 11,1945, by George Albert Smith, at age 48; died Dec. 13, 1953, at Los Angeles, Los Angeles Co., California, at age 56.